{"tid":1650150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（生日事件）今日不理 明日再談","createTime":"2019-10-12T22:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T23:35:52.000Z","uid":184739,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b304d581464540fdf66e228dd17251a15632d04c","tid":1650150,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T22:55:59.000Z","msg":"見到條片有人係太子靈堂前搞生日真係想割蓆,原來搞到自己最嬲係見到自己人做埋曬d左膠行為搞死自己人<br />\n<br />\n不過而家幾嬲幾想割都好,今日要團結行動,琴晚既事先忘記 單野星期一再慢慢處理或而家即時冷處理<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日係星期日要行動</span>,休息左好多日la,今日除左出街遍地花唔好花時間討論其他左膠行為,<span style=\"color: red;\">星期一再做檢討</span> <br />\n<br />\n我唔想咁樣完左個運動呀,有事就檢討,唔好諗住割蓆,今時今日大家坐同一條船,行左咁多個月,大家要知道4個月了,已經返唔到轉頭,今時今日只許勝不許敗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"cadeea059c4b3fc77300f4f8db93a94970ed124a","tid":1650150,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T22:56:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4982056e0843521a221143d8b50363250b7790e","tid":1650150,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T22:56:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88acf39a90ec0acfbceda2f8639dfa8578251dfc","tid":1650150,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T22:57:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"809bb4c5cdf37950d969f038492e51a7bf9559ff","tid":1650150,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T22:57:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32ac985bcb4c9dec5bbb2c99718b013db963088e","tid":1650150,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T22:58:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb78c895efa5ede735ffa7c9b52df2bb872eca31","tid":1650150,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T23:01:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9a8a3b880b4abdfa5931f27e913e8ca31ae62ed","tid":1650150,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T23:01:41.000Z","msg":